OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FStaying dry
OL,6,Ftonight with clear spells, however
OL,7,Fsome cloud will linger across the
OL,8,Fsouth of the region. A warm night, but
OL,9,Fcooler across parts of Cumbria as
OL,10,Ftemperatures dip into single figures.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FA largely dry and bright day
OL,13,Fwith plenty of sunny spells. A small
OL,14,Fchance of a few light showers later in
OL,15,Fthe afternoon. Feeling hot and
OL,16,Fincreasingly humid.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
